PF-I-cry    Core.sg boy
`The boy cried'

# correct plural determiner
Source: a:194
Vetted: s
Judgment: g
Phenomena: {det}
Nagsangit   dagiti  lalaki
n-ag-sangit dagiti  lalaki
PF-I-cry    Core.pl boy
`The boys cried'

