# Incorrect use of verbal arguments/transitivity.
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: u
Phenomena: {case}
Nagtudo iti balay
n-ag-tudo    iti       balay
PF-I-rain    Obl.sg    house
'It rained the house'

